    <item>
      <title>马克龙呼吁欧洲联合债券为国防和科技提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/macron-pledges-more-labor-reforms-and-pro-business-measures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统马克龙支持发行欧洲联合债券，用于支付国防和技术等优先事项，以确保欧洲在与中国和美国日益激烈的竞争中保持主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/macron-pledges-more-labor-reforms-and-pro-business-measures</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 17:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾计划在中国紧张局势中勘探富含石油的海域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/philippines-to-ramp-up-us-military-ties-amid-aggressive-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾最高国防官员表示，在与北京的紧张关系加剧之际，菲律宾正在与美国和其他安全伙伴建立防务联盟，以帮助为石油和天然气丰富的南海资源勘探铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/philippines-to-ramp-up-us-military-ties-amid-aggressive-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 11:21:03 GMT</pubDate>
